A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to motor vehicles; amending expiration and
2 renewal of licenses for persons under twenty-one (21) years
3 of age; amending identification card contents; clarifying
4 the timeline for contested case hearings regarding
5 licenses; amending requirements for replacement licenses;
6 adding a fee for replacement licenses; repealing obsolete
7 provisions; providing rulemaking authority; and providing
8 for effective dates.
