13 31-7-118. Replacement license.
14
15 (a) If a license issued under this act is lost,
16 destroyed or if the licensee desires to withdraw or insert
17 notice of anatomical organ donation or a medical alert
18 designation, the person may obtain the appropriate
19 replacement license upon payment of the proper fee and
20 surrender of the original license, if available.
